<dl class="gcf-lyt-detail-total">
<dt><span class="gcf-lyt-detail-total__title">支援人数</span></dt>
<dd><span class="gcf-lyt-detail-total__quantity">70</span><span class="gcf-lyt-detail-total__text">人</span></dd>
